Colin Jellicoe, HR Director
All our work on inclusion and diversity is designed to enable our people to 
maximise their abilities and contribution. 

Through our new ‘People Strategy’ we are looking at ways that we can ensure 
the effective development of all our people. 

Through compliance training, managing and fostering emerging talent and 
providing a structured employee development programme we are establishing 
a new culture within Morrison Utility Services ensuring that we develop our 
people and also create a structure that allows new entrants to our business to 
build a long lasting career with us. 

We recognise that our people are our greatest asset and we are committed to 
providing a stimulating working environment in which they can realise their full 
potential.

